We follow one man who has nothing left other than a beat up Camaro and a trunk full of guns and booze. 
He runs down Flesh Eaters, hunting for sport and redemption, while also running from his past. 
After crashing into a small group of survivors, who are running low on resources, he decides to lend a hand. 
But a surprise attack by the Flesh Eaters forces them on the run and puts the Hunter's skills to the test.
